sql.up: CREATE TABLE bb_c59lmqcph168hepgkv9oil4en4_atlnm6.subscription (id uuid DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(), title varchar(255) NOT NULL, website varchar(255), amount int NOT NULL CHECK (amount > 0), user_id uuid NOT NULL, currency varchar(255) NOT NULL, next_payment_date date NOT NULL, "interval" varchar(255) DEFAULT 'MONTH', frequency int NOT NULL DEFAULT '1', email_alert boolean DEFAULT '0', CONSTRAINT subscription_pkey PRIMARY KEY (id))
